{"tid":696232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國妹被魷魚口爆 精子狂咬","createTime":"2018-06-10T01:54:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T04:25:46.000Z","uid":72009,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"86189d4ca739a6556e54385834c2c791f12638d7","tid":696232,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"絕頂升天的口感！2012年一名韓國女子吃下烹煮過的魷魚後，口腔內忽出現劇烈疼痛，當時一度被懷疑是寄生蟲惹的禍，直到最近才有研究推翻了這項說法，原來這名女子是被魷魚口爆了，嘴裡的那些白色小點點正好就是魷魚的精子，專家提醒愛吃魷魚的民眾最好要將內臟清除乾淨、完全煮熟再食用比較安全。<br />\n<br />\n《太陽報》報導，韓國一名63歲的熟女幾年前吃下魷魚後疼痛莫名，嚇得她趕緊當場吐掉魷魚就醫，醫生檢查時在她牙齦、舌下與口腔內膜發現了12個紡錘形、疑似是寄生蟲的白色物體，但最近的醫學研究卻認為，那些白色物體應該就是魷魚的精蟲。<br />\n科學家指出，魷魚的精囊可依附在身體之外的地方，當天應該是魷魚沒煮熟，導致精囊內的精蟲沒死透，女子將精囊咬破後，精蟲進入嘴裡固定住導致她覺得嘴巴內有很多蟲子正在瘋狂啃咬，不過研究人員還不確定魷魚的精蟲是如何植入女子嘴裡的。無獨有偶，國際病理學雜誌也曾有一起類似案例，一名21歲的日本妹子在吃完魷魚後感到口腔劇痛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180610/1370493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370493&d=OzmwPigTyqvMq9bLATKCMDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=f5694234\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180610%2F1370493&h=bc9a5fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180610/1370493</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180610/640_475666fe0425b9118dae11c90fe80e86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180610%2F640_475666fe0425b9118dae11c90fe80e86.jpg&h=76e6dae6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f894921739b27313a5f7c951648d0af3bd4adbc5","tid":696232,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"精蟲瘋狂啃哎<br />\n咁交配時<br />\n隻雌性魷魚咪爽死"},{"pid":"804a23937f96966b6a8817b575b0342d2508e299","tid":696232,"uid":129521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:02:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">精蟲進入嘴裡固定住導致她覺得嘴巴內有很多蟲子正在瘋狂啃咬</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁口爆點算"},{"pid":"e5063eaa74f655ba322bfbceb216c512cf569a55","tid":696232,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"63歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37acf80eac7cb46d7d2a6bba5d72877f4db70b0","tid":696232,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7d3878e552aca7e5601677d0db30930fdf7cf2","tid":696232,"uid":120715,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"e5063eaa74f655ba322bfbceb216c512cf569a55","tid":696232,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"63歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"妹依個字究竟年齡界限由幾多歲至幾多歲"},{"pid":"db82cc7606d4c008940c3b74e961c8de3c6f10bd","tid":696232,"uid":33481,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8c7d3878e552aca7e5601677d0db30930fdf7cf2","tid":696232,"uid":120715,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"e5063eaa74f655ba322bfbceb216c512cf569a55","tid":696232,"uid":44333,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:13:56.000Z","msg":"63歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"妹依個字究竟年齡界限由幾多歲至幾多歲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T02:23:04.000Z","msg":"25或以上都唔應該用"},{"pid":"fb3ad69944123960c87ddfab10be763e8ef025fd","tid":696232,"uid":104454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"8c7d3878e552aca7e5601677d0db30930fdf7cf2","tid":696232,"uid":120715,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"e5063eaa74f65